{"id": "1206971713342935110", "channel_id": "1206971713342935110", "type": 0, "author_id": "1073914607741177866", "author_name": "scholar_2", "author_bot": false, "content": "一直等到57才打所以快ddl才打完，已經沒有什麽參考價值了，就當個記錄貼\n\n5：送很多力量，適合希洛發揮。道中切菜一樣，由於沒刷到星象儀導致boss戰二階段多凹了1小時暴擊；\n4：打防給特效，用上了雙子黑紅花。落地戰比較難打（有不間斷的封印很惡心）過了之後道中狂氣和產能轉起來就簡單了，boss戰比較難，紅花打莉莉較劣勢，需要卡著爆發時機連著不滅之花的盾一起打下去，最後依靠機制特攻卡掉二階段覺醒拿下；\n3：毒反觸發，只有一個毒隊的我就抬出栗子了。道中還算比較順利，boss戰面對鼠鼠，可能玩的不熟練or練度不夠，二階段的四連擊必須吃下才能拿下，以致於懲戒+淚珠還是只剩下19死抗；\n2：比較easy，用比較完善的圖珊希娜出陣。沒有精英的道中快速清完，boss戰打成分裂后壓力驟減，輕鬆拿下；\n1：更easy了，多段輸出量身定做，水母拖著凑人數的女僕鯊魚亂殺。", "timestamp": "2024-02-13T14:34:40.911000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1206971714303565894", "filename": "CTRFIW3FE8RE_A_5MU.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1722388, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1206971713342935110/1206971714303565894/CTRFIW3FE8RE_A_5MU.png?ex=69cbdb81&is=69ca8a01&hm=2314dabae30e404e89f7e3d806f4e87d7e5913fda8e76dd232467ab1d344fd63&"}, {"id": "1206971714983039049", "filename": "DJDWT_30JXPWKP3.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1791307, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1206971713342935110/1206971714983039049/DJDWT_30JXPWKP3.png?ex=69cbdb81&is=69ca8a01&hm=2356ce6bd72e2564d25bbae140622b47aeeb394cbaa669a8b4c87ee693c92586&"}, {"id": "1206971715561988226", "filename": "A3HLO3WLDT6_6OQCGCXY.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1873162, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1206971713342935110/1206971715561988226/A3HLO3WLDT6_6OQCGCXY.png?ex=69cbdb81&is=69ca8a01&hm=98a03ce2fd1265c485805c53efcc210aef0c928d87dbe2d1f19d6838542b4cae&"}, {"id": "1206971716220489788", "filename": "6F_R1VAZJLTK3MHU52BFN2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1736506, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1206971713342935110/1206971716220489788/6F_R1VAZJLTK3MHU52BFN2.png?ex=69cbdb81&is=69ca8a01&hm=0217b07e08e0622adc1c816205032f7d73